..."Buenaventura", a bonus CD featuring ten tracks handpicked from Phish's March 21, 1993 Ventura Theatre show.


---------------------------------------
Extra info (full show NOT included in this torrent):
Sunday, 03/21/1993
Ventura Theatre, Ventura, CA

Set 1: Maze, Sparkle, The Sloth, Divided Sky, Esther[1] > All Things Reconsidered, Split Open and Melt, Poor Heart, Punch You In the Eye, Lawn Boy > Possum[2]

Set 2: Loving Cup, My Friend, My Friend[3], Rift > Tweezer[4] > Ya Mar, Llama, You Enjoy Myself, My Sweet One > Big Ball Jam, Hold Your Head Up > Cracklin' Rosie > Hold Your Head Up, Harry Hood, Cavern

Encore: Sleeping Monkey, Sweet Adeline[5], Tweezer Reprise

[1] Random Note signal in intro.
[2] Simpsons signal.
[3] Beginning featured Trey on acoustic guitar. No "Myfe" ending.
[4] Walk This Way teases.
[5] Without microphones.

Notes: The Esther intro contained a Random Note signal and Possum contained a Simpsons signal. The beginning of My Friend featured Trey on acoustic guitar. My Friend did not contain the "Myfe" ending. Tweezer contained Walk This Way teases. Sweet Adeline was performed without microphones.
